summary: AN ORDINANCE transferring partial jurisdiction over certain City (Department of Parks and Recreation) property in Block 1, Minor's Addition, Block 101, Plat of Seattle Tide Lands and government Lot 4 of Section 22, Township 25 North, Range 3 East, W.M. to permit the construction and maintenance of a sanitary sewer with appurtenances. (West Galer Street, et al, Sanitary Sewer)
